OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776881467
OL,3,CManchester Airport gets all night
OL,4,Ctrain service
OL,6,FTrains will run all night to
OL,7,FManchester Airport in a major new
OL,8,Ftimetable shakeup.
OL,10,FTransPennine Express (TPE) will
OL,11,Fintroduce eight new services which
OL,12,Fwill mean there will be a train
OL,13,Froughly every hour between Manchester
OL,14,FPiccadilly and Manchester Airport all
OL,15,Fday, every day.
OL,17,FAlongside the rest of the rail
OL,18,Findustry, the train operator will
OL,19,Fintroduce a new timetable from Sunday
OL,20,F17 May.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
