OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776881467
OL,3,CManchester Airport gets all night
OL,4,Ctrain service
OL,6,FThe move is aimed at improving
OL,7,Fconnectivity for passengers travelling
OL,8,Fearly in the morning or late at night,
OL,9,Fparticularly those flying in and out
OL,10,Fof the UK's thirdbusiest airport.
OL,12,FTPE will also introduce an additional
OL,13,Fweekday call at Dewsbury on the 8.05am
OL,14,FLeeds to Manchester Piccadilly service.
OL,16,FThe stop is new to the timetable and
OL,17,Fis expected to support students and
OL,18,Fcommuters travelling into Manchester,
OL,19,Foffering greater flexibility for
OL,20,Fearlymorning journeys.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
