PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776881467
OL,3,CManchester Airport gets all night
OL,4,Ctrain service
OL,6,FAndrew McClements, Customer Experience
OL,7,F& Transformation Director at TPE,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Although most of our services
OL,9,Fare unchanged, we encourage customers
OL,10,Fto take a moment to check any journeys
OL,11,Fthey make regularly.
OL,13,F"We're pleased to be introducing
OL,14,Fservices that give customers more
OL,15,Fchoice, added flexibility, and an
OL,16,Fimproved overall experience when
OL,17,Ftravelling with us."
OL,26,@pD@GOUuD@AOUyD@TO]
